01:19:57.411 --> 01:19:59.330
Lagal si! Zbudi se!

01:20:01.415 --> 01:20:02.830
Zbudi se!

01:20:03.083 --> 01:20:04.498
Zbudi se!

01:20:05.920 --> 01:20:07.335
Zdaj te potrebujem!

01:20:21.142 --> 01:20:23.561
Poškodoval se boš, če boš tako
nadaljeval. –Ni pomagalo!

01:20:23.728 --> 01:20:26.564
Rekel si, da bo drevo tise
pomagalo, vendar ni!

01:20:26.731 --> 01:20:28.146
Ozdravi jo! Naj ji bo bolje!

01:20:28.858 --> 01:20:30.273
Conor!

01:20:30.985 --> 01:20:33.029
Ti si poklical mene,
Conor O'Malley.

01:20:33.196 --> 01:20:35.281
Če sem te jaz klical,
sem te, da jo rešiš!

01:20:35.448 --> 01:20:38.493
Da jo ozdraviš!
–Nisem prišel zdraviti nje.

01:20:38.660 --> 01:20:42.247
Ja, si!
–Zdraviti sem prišel tebe. –Mene?

01:20:42.580 --> 01:20:44.707
Jaz ne potrebujem zdravljenja!

01:20:45.250 --> 01:20:48.211
Kolikokrat še ti naj povem?

01:20:48.878 --> 01:20:50.712
Moja mama ga potrebuje.

01:21:04.518 --> 01:21:05.933
Pomagaj mi.

01:21:13.110 --> 01:21:15.112
Prišel je čas za četrto zgodbo.

01:21:18.740 --> 01:21:19.782
Ne!

01:21:19.783 --> 01:21:21.450
Ne, prosim! Spravi me stran!

01:21:21.617 --> 01:21:23.119
Čas je za tvojo nočno moro.

01:21:23.286 --> 01:21:24.912
Nazaj k mami moram!

01:21:25.329 --> 01:21:27.331
Je že tukaj.

01:21:32.878 --> 01:21:33.795
Ne!

01:21:33.796 --> 01:21:35.214
Mama, pojdi stran!

01:21:35.381 --> 01:21:36.796
V redu je!

01:21:36.924 --> 01:21:39.135
Vse je v redu.
Ni potrebe za skrb.

01:21:39.302 --> 01:21:41.053
Mama, zbeži!
Prosim, zbeži stran!

01:21:43.472 --> 01:21:44.887
Mama!

01:21:52.647 --> 01:21:54.062
Mama!

01:21:58.403 --> 01:21:59.818
Conor!

